classDiagram
    class MermaidDirective {
        +run() list~Node~
    }
    class mermaid_inline {
        +mermaid_source str
    }
    class Renderer {
        +render(source, theme) str
        -cache Path
    }
    MermaidDirective --> mermaid_inline : emits
    mermaid_inline --> Renderer : rendered by
